Atom_LinkCountHigh Property

CDXML Name:LinkCountHigh
CDX Constant Name:kCDXProp_Atom_LinkCountHigh
CDX Constant Value:0x043E
Data Size:INT16
Property of objects:kCDXObj_Node
First written/read in:ChemDraw 7.0
Required?No

Description:

High end of repeat count for link nodes.

This property is meaningful only for nodes with a kCDXProp_Node_Type of type LinkNode.

If this property is absent:

The LinkCountHigh is assumed to be 1.
